Key Match Events: Astros beat Diamondbacks 8-1 to earn third straight AL West title
Jose Altuve and Yordan Alvarez each homered in the game
Post-Match Reflections: The Astros celebrated clinching a playoff spot with T-shirts and a subdued toast
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the third game in the series between the Astros and Diamondbacks, with the Astros winning all three
Others: The game took place at Chase Field in Phoenix, Arizona
